1
00:01:49,600 --> 00:01:50,479
Lord Su.

2
00:01:50,920 --> 00:01:53,440
Your crimes are heinous.

3
00:01:53,680 --> 00:01:55,080
The Emperor is furious.

4
00:01:55,560 --> 00:01:57,620
You have no one to blame but yourself.

5
00:02:16,920 --> 00:02:19,920
The guilty official, Su Ziliang, has been executed.

6
00:02:19,920 --> 00:02:22,120
All men shall be executed.

7
00:02:22,120 --> 00:02:24,780
All women shall be sold as official courtesans.

8
00:02:56,560 --> 00:02:57,360
Zhaoxue.

9
00:02:57,880 --> 00:03:01,360
Qihong Tower is busiest at this time.

10
00:03:02,320 --> 00:03:03,720
It's crowded.

11
00:03:04,320 --> 00:03:05,850
Perfect for saving Yan'er.

12
00:03:06,520 --> 00:03:08,240
I've asked around.

13
00:03:08,320 --> 00:03:10,560
Yan'er is in the second room upstairs.

14
00:03:10,920 --> 00:03:11,520
Good work.

15
00:03:13,880 --> 00:03:15,120
Does it have to be today?

16
00:03:15,120 --> 00:03:18,160
I heard the Dragon Shadow Guard is about to seal this place.

17
00:03:18,160 --> 00:03:19,160
It must be today.

18
00:03:20,720 --> 00:03:21,720
After today,

19
00:03:21,880 --> 00:03:22,880
Yan'er will be...

20
00:03:25,280 --> 00:03:27,160
Brother Li, you should go.

21
00:03:27,840 --> 00:03:29,440
Don't risk yourself with me.

22
00:03:30,960 --> 00:03:33,800
Then I won't get in your way.

23
00:03:33,800 --> 00:03:35,240
I'm slow on my feet.

24
00:03:35,280 --> 00:03:36,560
Be careful.

25
00:03:37,280 --> 00:03:38,320
Don't worry.

26
00:03:39,360 --> 00:03:40,160
I'm going.

27
00:03:41,520 --> 00:03:46,320
Okay.

28
00:03:46,960 --> 00:03:51,280
Okay.

29
00:04:36,320 --> 00:04:37,040
See no evil.

30
00:04:37,120 --> 00:04:37,920
See no evil.

31
00:04:41,920 --> 00:04:43,050
Who are you? Get out!

32
00:04:49,400 --> 00:04:49,860
Yan'er.

33
00:04:54,840 --> 00:04:55,300
Yan'er.

34
00:04:56,720 --> 00:04:57,650
What do you want?

35
00:05:05,720 --> 00:05:06,920
Why are you standing there? Chase her!

36
00:05:06,920 --> 00:05:07,480
Yes!

37
00:05:08,720 --> 00:05:09,520
Go!

38
00:05:28,000 --> 00:05:29,200
Don't let her escape!

39
00:05:30,000 --> 00:05:30,440
Yes!

40
00:05:35,560 --> 00:05:36,220
Go that way!

41
00:05:41,760 --> 00:05:42,440
Move!

42
00:05:53,600 --> 00:05:54,360
Lord Fang.

43
00:05:55,280 --> 00:05:55,920
Pi Hu.

44
00:05:56,800 --> 00:05:58,130
What are you doing here?

45
00:05:59,560 --> 00:06:00,840
I am acting on Imperial orders

46
00:06:00,840 --> 00:06:03,300
to capture a fugitive attempting to escape.

47
00:06:03,600 --> 00:06:04,160
But,

48
00:06:05,280 --> 00:06:07,400
why are you here, Lord Fang?

49
00:06:09,440 --> 00:06:11,170
As the Right Censor-in-Chief,

50
00:06:11,280 --> 00:06:13,540
do I need to report my whereabouts to you?

51
00:06:15,040 --> 00:06:16,120
I wouldn't dare.

52
00:06:16,440 --> 00:06:21,440
I just saw the suspect slip in here with my own eyes.

53
00:06:22,480 --> 00:06:23,610
I came to arrest her.

54
00:06:24,280 --> 00:06:26,080
Then search carefully.

55
00:06:27,280 --> 00:06:29,200
To avoid loose talk.

56
00:06:31,320 --> 00:06:33,720
I have already checked.

57
00:06:33,800 --> 00:06:37,200
There is no one else here with you, Lord Fang.

58
00:06:38,280 --> 00:06:39,409
I will take my leave.

59
00:06:47,840 --> 00:06:49,000
Come out.

60
00:06:50,320 --> 00:06:51,480
Who are you?

61
00:07:02,320 --> 00:07:03,760
I didn't expect to meet you here today,

62
00:07:03,760 --> 00:07:05,290
and witness your demeanor.

63
00:07:05,640 --> 00:07:08,320
It is a pity I am a woman.

64
00:07:08,400 --> 00:07:09,930
I fear you might despise me.

65
00:07:10,200 --> 00:07:10,920
You are busy, my lord.

66
00:07:10,920 --> 00:07:12,320
I shouldn't disturb you further.

67
00:07:12,320 --> 00:07:13,450
I will take my leave.

68
00:07:19,400 --> 00:07:21,640
She is related to Lord Su Ziliang.

69
00:07:31,840 --> 00:07:32,600
Move! Move!

70
00:07:32,720 --> 00:07:34,450
Dragon Shadow Guard business!

71
00:08:00,760 --> 00:08:03,160
You stopped searching when you saw Fang Ji?

72
00:08:03,200 --> 00:08:05,840
What if he's harboring the criminal?

73
00:08:06,400 --> 00:08:08,080
I was afraid of offending Lord Fang.

74
00:08:08,080 --> 00:08:09,720
If he goes before the Emperor later,

75
00:08:09,720 --> 00:08:11,320
and impeaches the Northern Judicial Office,

76
00:08:11,320 --> 00:08:13,880
it would be very troublesome.

77
00:08:16,720 --> 00:08:19,320
He makes things difficult for me at every turn.

78
00:08:19,480 --> 00:08:20,680
This is outrageous!

79
00:08:21,080 --> 00:08:23,280
Oh, my goodness.

80
00:08:23,680 --> 00:08:26,200
I didn't know the Young Marquis was gracing Qihong Tower with his presence.

81
00:08:26,200 --> 00:08:28,080
And with such a large force.

82
00:08:28,360 --> 00:08:30,480
Is there some misunderstanding?

83
00:08:33,720 --> 00:08:34,850
Misunderstanding?

84
00:08:35,720 --> 00:08:39,240
Your Qihong Tower conspired with the criminal Huang Wansan

85
00:08:39,600 --> 00:08:41,799
with the intention of plunging the world into chaos.

86
00:08:41,799 --> 00:08:45,320
Now, you have incurred His Majesty's wrath.

87
00:08:46,480 --> 00:08:47,400
Oh my.

88
00:08:47,440 --> 00:08:50,320
We are innocent. The people who come here

89
00:08:50,320 --> 00:08:53,200
are all prominent figures in the capital.

90
00:08:53,200 --> 00:08:54,880
How could there be criminals?

91
00:08:55,200 --> 00:08:59,200
Young Marquis, please don't wrong innocent people.

92
00:08:59,720 --> 00:09:03,080
If you disturb the guests' enjoyment,

93
00:09:03,680 --> 00:09:08,600
even the Northern Bureau cannot bear the responsibility.

94
00:09:25,080 --> 00:09:26,160
Who goes there?

95
00:09:30,320 --> 00:09:32,850
Ruilang, how can you hurt people so casually?

96
00:09:33,200 --> 00:09:34,200
This is nonsense.

97
00:09:34,680 --> 00:09:35,680
Fang Ji.

98
00:09:36,080 --> 00:09:37,940
It's not your place to lecture me.

99
00:09:38,720 --> 00:09:40,600
You are a court official,

100
00:09:41,240 --> 00:09:43,720
yet you dare to seek pleasure at Qihong Tower.

101
00:09:43,720 --> 00:09:46,480
My Censorate has the duty of supervision.

102
00:09:46,680 --> 00:09:48,920
You Dragon Shadow Guards are always reckless.

103
00:09:48,920 --> 00:09:50,200
I came here early

104
00:09:50,440 --> 00:09:52,120
naturally to supervise you.

105
00:09:56,000 --> 00:09:57,680
You oppose me at every turn.

106
00:09:58,240 --> 00:10:00,770
You just want to show off in front of my father.

107
00:10:01,600 --> 00:10:02,520
Childish.

108
00:10:06,600 --> 00:10:07,000
Speak.

109
00:10:07,520 --> 00:10:08,650
Who on earth are you?

110
00:10:08,680 --> 00:10:10,120
She is my protégé.

111
00:10:13,120 --> 00:10:14,640
I am Gu Lihan,

112
00:10:14,800 --> 00:10:15,930
from Yuhang County.

113
00:10:16,880 --> 00:10:19,720
Fortunately, Lord Fang did not mind that I am a woman

114
00:10:19,720 --> 00:10:21,450
and recruited me as an advisor.

115
00:10:23,640 --> 00:10:26,920
Lord Fang is indeed my father's good disciple.

116
00:10:27,520 --> 00:10:29,720
He actually chose a woman as an advisor.

117
00:10:30,280 --> 00:10:31,680
I just wonder,

118
00:10:31,680 --> 00:10:35,640
what His Majesty and the officials will think when they find out.

119
00:10:35,840 --> 00:10:37,880
As long as one can serve our dynasty,

120
00:10:38,120 --> 00:10:40,640
gender does not matter.

121
00:10:42,240 --> 00:10:45,640
Then what special talents does this young lady have?

122
00:10:46,240 --> 00:10:47,480
I am of humble talent,

123
00:10:47,680 --> 00:10:50,280
but I happen to be known as the 'Jianghu Know-it-all'.

124
00:10:50,280 --> 00:10:52,000
I dare say in the whole Jianghu,

125
00:10:52,000 --> 00:10:53,930
no one is better informed than I am.

126
00:10:55,520 --> 00:10:57,050
If you have nothing to hide,

127
00:10:57,400 --> 00:10:59,880
then why did you run just now?

128
00:11:00,720 --> 00:11:01,520
Pihu.

129
00:11:01,520 --> 00:11:01,920
Here.

130
00:11:02,520 --> 00:11:03,320
Take her away.

131
00:11:04,640 --> 00:11:05,440
Take her away.

132
00:11:19,800 --> 00:11:20,600
Speak.

133
00:11:21,880 --> 00:11:23,040
Who exactly are you?

134
00:11:24,800 --> 00:11:27,000
Ruilang, have you forgotten?

135
00:11:27,120 --> 00:11:28,720
I told you last night,

136
00:11:29,440 --> 00:11:30,920
she is my protégé.

137
00:11:32,080 --> 00:11:33,920
Even if she is your protégé,

138
00:11:35,840 --> 00:11:37,770
what was she doing at Qihong Tower?

139
00:11:39,840 --> 00:11:42,170
She doesn't have the duty to supervise me.

140
00:11:43,120 --> 00:11:44,720
To answer the Young Marquis,

141
00:11:44,840 --> 00:11:46,040
to tell you the truth,

142
00:11:46,400 --> 00:11:48,600
I went to find my younger sister.

143
00:11:50,000 --> 00:11:52,080
My family has been poor since I was young.

144
00:11:52,080 --> 00:11:55,080
My sister was tricked and abducted into Qihong Tower.

145
00:11:55,640 --> 00:11:57,480
I have always wanted to redeem her,

146
00:11:57,480 --> 00:11:59,280
but I hadn't saved enough money.

147
00:12:00,160 --> 00:12:02,720
Last night, I was desperate to see her.

148
00:12:03,360 --> 00:12:05,220
That is why I went to Qihong Tower.

149
00:12:06,320 --> 00:12:07,120
Sister?

150
00:12:09,120 --> 00:12:10,650
What is your sister's name?

151
00:12:11,920 --> 00:12:15,050
Ruilang, instead of rushing to track down the criminal,

152
00:12:15,120 --> 00:12:17,200
you are fixated on a girl.

153
00:12:17,640 --> 00:12:20,280
Besides, she is my protégé.

154
00:12:20,600 --> 00:12:22,040
I will report to His Majesty

155
00:12:22,040 --> 00:12:23,480
to have this case transferred to someone else.

156
00:12:23,480 --> 00:12:25,040
To avoid wasting time.

157
00:12:26,920 --> 00:12:28,320
I'll believe you for now.

158
00:12:30,480 --> 00:12:31,680
Bring in the next one.

159
00:12:40,720 --> 00:12:42,200
Lord Censor.

160
00:12:42,200 --> 00:12:43,060
Young Marquis.

161
00:12:43,480 --> 00:12:45,480
Please do justice for me.

162
00:12:45,480 --> 00:12:46,920
I am innocent.

163
00:12:49,720 --> 00:12:50,760
My Lord.

164
00:12:50,880 --> 00:12:52,760
You must do justice for me.

165
00:12:53,640 --> 00:12:55,240
This dancer from the Western Regions

166
00:12:55,240 --> 00:12:57,500
is clearly Huang Wansan's subordinate.

167
00:12:58,120 --> 00:13:00,320
Huang Wansan did stay with me.

168
00:13:00,960 --> 00:13:01,360
But...

169
00:13:01,840 --> 00:13:03,520
before the Dragon Guards arrived,

170
00:13:03,520 --> 00:13:05,120
he went to see this dancer.

171
00:13:05,280 --> 00:13:06,480
They spotted me

172
00:13:06,520 --> 00:13:08,380
and tried to kill me to silence me.

173
00:13:11,720 --> 00:13:12,720
I only know how to dance.

174
00:13:12,720 --> 00:13:14,120
I don't know martial arts.

175
00:13:14,120 --> 00:13:15,280
When chaos broke out in Qihong Tower,

176
00:13:15,280 --> 00:13:18,040
I just wanted to leave with Lady Hua, who knows martial arts.

177
00:13:18,040 --> 00:13:20,300
I didn't expect to be caught by you lords.

178
00:13:20,520 --> 00:13:22,520
I don't know why Lady Hua would say that.

179
00:13:22,520 --> 00:13:23,520
You're lying!

180
00:13:23,520 --> 00:13:25,120
Your martial arts skills are clearly good.

181
00:13:25,120 --> 00:13:25,920
Silence!

182
00:13:30,040 --> 00:13:30,900
Young Marquis.

183
00:13:31,120 --> 00:13:31,840
Lord Fang.

184
00:13:33,120 --> 00:13:33,780
Last night,

185
00:13:34,000 --> 00:13:35,920
these two tried to escape from Qihong Tower.

186
00:13:35,920 --> 00:13:37,200
My brothers and I caught them

187
00:13:37,200 --> 00:13:39,320
and brought them back to the Northern Fusi.

188
00:13:39,320 --> 00:13:41,440
They haven't stopped arguing since.

189
00:13:42,400 --> 00:13:43,200
Gu Lihan.

190
00:13:44,440 --> 00:13:47,040
You claim to be the Know-It-All of the Jianghu,

191
00:13:47,040 --> 00:13:48,640
and well-versed in its affairs.

192
00:13:48,640 --> 00:13:50,440
Why don't you interrogate them?

193
00:13:51,320 --> 00:13:51,850
Yes, sir.

194
00:13:53,960 --> 00:13:55,290
Strip these two dancers

195
00:13:55,320 --> 00:13:56,360
of their clothes.
